author: Five Star Professional Representative
title: Five Star Professional Honors Joshua Hoffschneider of COUNTRY Financial with
text:
Joshua Hoffschneider, COUNTRY Financial will be featured issue of Phoenix Magazine as a 2015 Five Star Wealth Manager award winner. identify and showcase an exclusive group of wealth managers who have demonstrated excellence in their field.
“I am truly honored to receive the Five Star Wealth Manager award! To me, this award reflects my passion for always putting the client’s needs first. My mission is to help the client achieve financial security for their retirement. I would not be where I am today without the help and trust of my clients. To them I say: “Thank you for entrusting me with your financial future! It is a burden that I will never take lightly,” says Joshua Hoffschneider of COUNTRY Financial.
Joshua Hoffschneider
